        the remote host is printed. If --oo is given, the office location and
        phone number are printed instead (the default).
        Idle time is in minutes if it is a single integer, hours and minutes
        if a colon (::) is present, or days if a dd is present. Login time is
        displayed as the day name if fewer than six days. It is displayed as
        month, day, hours, and minutes, unless more than six months ago, in
